### How to use
1. Open `Webhook` node and copy the `Production URL`
2. Activate the workflow
3. In a web browser, PostMan or n8n HTTP Request invoke the Production URL: `{prod url}?ytID={youtube ID}`. 
e.g. `{your instance URL}/webhook/youtube-engaging-moments-extractor?ytID=IZsQqarWXtYy`
